            I muſt deſire the patient reader, to heare a little further of this Preachers blaſphemie, more incredible than ye reſt, wherein he doth prophane the principalleſt myſterie of our Chriſtian religion. And is, Quamuis ab aeterno Deus praedestinauerit, 
               
